videos.headline: Woolfolk scores 13-yard Troy TD
videos.description: Kaleb Barker completes a shovel pass to Trevon Woolfolk for a 13-yard touchdown to give Troy a 7-3 lead over Texas State.

videos.headline: Brown breaks free for 21-yard Texas State TD
videos.description: Robert Brown Jr. takes the handoff and dashes up the field to score a 21-yard touchdown for Texas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown breaks free for 21-yard Texas State TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barker finds Todd for 38-yard Troy TD
videos.description: Kaleb Barker connects with Reggie Todd across the middle to score a 38-yard touchdown and give Troy a 21-10 lead over Texas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Barker finds Todd for 38-yard Troy TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET
